{"tid":2368671,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新福爾摩斯1-4","createTime":"2021-01-16T11:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T18:18:47.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71ac2b5b33b07a793f5abdfaac800f6fb0ddc7af","tid":2368671,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=96cf1651\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=00f05bc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=6dcb4055\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/tsukadagoseki/1483363519-2077212025_n.jpg?v=1483363626\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftsukadagoseki%2F1483363519-2077212025_n.jpg%3Fv%3D1483363626&h=9b0c9d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《新世紀福爾摩斯》（英語：Sherlock）是一部英國 BBC 電視連續劇，改編自亞瑟&middot;柯南&middot;道爾爵士的夏洛克&middot;福爾摩斯偵探小說。<br />\n本劇編劇為史蒂芬&middot;莫法特和馬克&middot;加蒂斯。由班奈狄克&middot;康柏拜區飾演夏洛克&middot;福爾摩斯，馬丁&middot;費里曼飾演約翰&middot;華生。繼2009年末播出的試播集之後，各90分鐘的第一季三集在2010年7月、8月於英國廣播公司第一台和英國廣播公司高清台播放；第二季的三集於2012年1月播放，並於同年5月在美國的英國廣播公司美國台和PBS公共電視網頻道播放[3]。第三季則於2014年1月1日開始在英國播出[4]，並取得平均達1182萬人次的收視率，成為英國自2001年以來，收視率最高的電視影集[5]。這部影集已在超過200個國家及地區播放..<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=731e5b5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=c52721e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9212e1941e72e9a908a3763e903939202a97a","tid":2368671,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf55e0ffd899856b508d2a44ca9d11f7be179d4","tid":2368671,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92b7b03bf0d7b3655f8e75e